### Creation of the CONSUMO_ACTUAL board from cnmc_sips, viesgo_begasa_sips and contracts

msg.data: Creation of the CONSUMO_ACTUAL board from cnmc_sips, viesgo_begasa_sips and contracts

paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE TABLE CONSUMO_ACTUAL AS
SELECT sipsco.cups, contracts.numcontrato, contracts.fcontrato, contracts.codproducto, contracts.email, contracts.codpostal, 
       sips.distribuidora, sips.coddist, sips.falta, sips.tarifa as tarifa_sips, sips.tensionps, sips.fases, sips.potmaxbie, 
       sips.perfilree, sips.potcontrp1, sips.potcontrp2, sips.potcontrp3, sips.potcontrp4, sips.potcontrp5, sips.potcontrp6, sips.potmaxp1, sips.potmaxp2,
       sips.potmaxp3, sips.potmaxp4, sips.potmaxp5, sips.potmaxp6, sipsco.finicio, sipsco.ffin, sipsco.tarifa as tarifa_sipsco, sipsco.consumoactivap1,
       sipsco.consumoactivap2, sipsco.consumoactivap3, sipsco.consumoactivap4, sipsco.consumoactivap5, sipsco.consumoactivap6, sipsco.numdias, sipsco.cmd
FROM (
    SELECT sco.cups, sco.finicio, sco.ffin, sco.tarifa, sco.consumoactivap1, sco.consumoactivap2, sco.consumoactivap3, sco.consumoactivap4, sco.consumoactivap5, sco.consumoactivap6, sco.numdias, sco.cmd
    FROM sipsco AS sco
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT cups, MAX(finicio) AS last_finicio, MAX(ffin) AS last_ffin
        FROM sipsco
        GROUP BY cups
    ) AS last_dates ON sco.cups = last_dates.cups AND sco.finicio = last_dates.last_finicio AND sco.ffin = last_dates.last_ffin
) AS sipsco
JOIN sips ON sipsco.cups = sips.cups
JOIN contracts ON sipsco.cups = contracts.cups
